  "texts": [
    "Moreover, users believe receiving an explanation and a recommendation will help them understand how their data is being used and processed in the system.",
    "Therefore, explainable recommendations can potentially help reduce users' fear of online insecurity regarding personal data usage.",
    "The notion of \"reasoning with the system for changing decisions\" refers to users' eagerness to use the explanation to converse with the system so that the system can learn and change decisions according to the users' interests.",
    "Additionally, as part of the conversation, users want to have the opportunity to reason in layperson's terms rather than using technologyspecific words.",
    "After that, as part of RQ2, we explore \"How do users want the explanations to be presented/ delivered to them?\""
  ],
